casebody.data:
Helen R. GODDARD and Malcolm S. Goddard, husband and wife, Plaintiffs-Petitioners,
v.
Joseph I. FINK, Jr. and Atlantic City Electric Company, d/b/a Atlantic City Electric, a PHI company, a New Jersey Corporation, Defendants-Respondents. C-737 September Term 2018
082035 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 21, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002866-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
